{"tid":1150563,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今日老母節 祝全天下老母……","createTime":"2019-05-12T02:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-12T14:12:06.000Z","uid":34777,"like":39,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b5470e0ad76bd99a369b5f9830f88f9cade12a49","tid":1150563,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:51:16.000Z","msg":"今日5月12號係老母節嘅大日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n平時大家對住老母都怕怕醜醜 唔敢表達愛意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日就係一個好機會同老母講句我愛你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ozv7Rcx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOzv7Rcx.jpg&h=afa4f6c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今朝起身嘅時候 不妨同老母講一聲: 平時辛苦啦 <br />\n再唔係send一張長輩圖比老母<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nJ6rngq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnJ6rngq.jpg&h=5fa6a88a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n話比老母知你有幾愛佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n或者有時候 一句說話可以為你帶嚟老母對你滿滿滿嘅愛意<del>以後老母都有求必應<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></del><br />\n祝成為老母嘅絲打 今日老母節快樂！！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lvd1VC3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLvd1VC3.png&h=c39927bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n未成為老母嘅/ 唔會做到老母 淨係會做到老豆嘅<br />\n記得一起身就對自己老母講聲我愛你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eYPMniY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeYPMniY.jpg&h=87ff8d30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最後祝全天下老母 老母節快樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今朝起身我錫咗老母一啖啦 你今日錫咗未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5218f8ffb7c753b2942786d5a00997f232b4fb5d","tid":1150563,"uid":198583,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:54:02.000Z","msg":"我到左牙媽碗湯，是否不孝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18d0b7f99f614e0226d48dc4bb91280e06d0909d","tid":1150563,"uid":34777,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:54:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日大家要好好愛護老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4287ab55795da81024e9c032fcc44f4d4c478b33","tid":1150563,"uid":34777,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"5218f8ffb7c753b2942786d5a00997f232b4fb5d","tid":1150563,"uid":198583,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:54:02.000Z","msg":"我到左牙媽碗湯，是否不孝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T02:55:10.000Z","msg":"你打5p字都不孝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2169ea1ef72b4730c3e89b2752a777e896586354","tid":1150563,"uid":100406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T03:00:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a92e1bc4af5934861fb7eb453504881f19509e0","tid":1150563,"uid":34777,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-12T03:01:00.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i